OL,3,CTom Lockyer returns to Bristol Rovers
OL,4,Ctwo years after cardiac arrest
OL,6,FBristol Rovers Head Coach Darrell
OL,7,FClarke says former Premier League
OL,8,Fplayer Tom Lockyer is "ready to go" as
OL,9,Fhe returns to his boyhood club.
OL,11,FThe centre-back suffered a cardiac
OL,12,Farrest whilst playing for Luton Town
OL,13,Fagainst Bournemouth at the Vitality
OL,14,FStadium in December 2023. He's not
OL,15,Fplayed a professional game since.
OL,17,FAfter signing a contract until the end
OL,18,Fof the season, the 30-year-old said:
OL,19,F"It's about coming home and playing
OL,20,Ffootball.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/6
