OL,3,CTom Lockyer returns to Bristol Rovers
OL,4,Ctwo years after cardiac arrest
OL,6,F"It is only really today where I've
OL,7,Fallowed myself to get really excited
OL,8,Fbecause until it's signed, sealed and
OL,9,Fdelivered, you always think something
OL,10,Fmight go wrong.
OL,12,F"It is so hard to explain, but it's
OL,13,Feverything I've worked so hard for
OL,14,Fover the last two years. Hopefully, I
OL,15,Fcan have many, many more good memories
OL,16,Fin a football shirt.
