OL,3,CTom Lockyer returns to Bristol Rovers
OL,4,Ctwo years after cardiac arrest
OL,6,F"I'm doing this because I love playing
OL,7,Ffootball and I've got that massive
OL,8,Fdesire to play football again, and
OL,9,Fwhat better place to do that than back
OL,10,Fhome."
OL,12,FCardiff-born Lockyer signed a
OL,13,Fscholarship with the Gas in 2011 and
OL,14,Fmade his debut for the club in a 3-0
OL,15,Fwin against Fleetwood Town. He scored
OL,16,Fhis first league goal in August 2013,
OL,17,Fthree months after signing his first
OL,18,Fprofessional contract.
