OL,3,CTom Lockyer returns to Bristol Rovers
OL,4,Ctwo years after cardiac arrest
OL,6,FThe 30-year-old made nearly 300
OL,7,Fappearances for the club before
OL,8,Fjoining Championship side Charlton
OL,9,FAthletic in the summer of 2019.
OL,11,F15 months later, Lockyer joined the
OL,12,FHatters and became captain in the 2022/
OL,13,F23 season after earning a spot in the
OL,14,FEFL Championship Team of the Season.
OL,16,FThe Wales international scored the
OL,17,Fgoal that confirmed Luton Town's place
OL,18,Fin the Championship Play-Off Final, in
OL,19,Fwhich they went on to secure promotion
OL,20,Fto the Premier League for the first
OL,21,Ftime.
