OL,3,CTom Lockyer returns to Bristol Rovers
OL,4,Ctwo years after cardiac arrest
OL,6,FRovers boss Darrell Clarke, who
OL,7,Fresigned with the club in the summer,
OL,8,Fsays his new defender is "coming in to
OL,9,Fwin".
OL,11,FHe said: "He could quite easily sit at
OL,12,Fhome or on a beach somewhere and enjoy
OL,13,Fthe rest of his life, but his football
OL,14,Fis his life and getting him back here
OL,15,Fwas a great moment for him and for us.
