OL,3,CTom Lockyer returns to Bristol Rovers
OL,4,Ctwo years after cardiac arrest
OL,6,F"Ricky Martin, the medical team, the
OL,7,Fowners, everybody has done a
OL,8,Ftremendous amount of work to get this
OL,9,Fover the line. So, it's a big thank
OL,10,Fyou from me because I think he'll be a
OL,11,Fvery, very useful addition to our
OL,12,Fsquad."
OL,14,FSpeaking about Tom's medical, he
OL,15,Fadded: "The testing and everything he
OL,16,Fhas gone through and his family has
OL,17,Fgone through; they live that
OL,18,Fjourney... He's had to pass so many
OL,19,Ftests to be able to get himself back
OL,20,Fplaying."
